race.comment: ANALYZATION (8) recorded a 6 length win (25.37) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Unbeaten in two runs from this draw. Looks the one to beat with even luck. JED'S MEMORY (6) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (25.58) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. GOLD CLASS COOL (4) finished in the money three on end before breaking through for an overdue win last start (30.16) at The Meadows. Has a good record at this journey. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. Something for the Multiples: BAG OF SNAGS (1)
